{"id":9741,"date":"2012-11-10T11:36:09","date_gmt":"2012-11-10T16:36:09","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=9741"},"modified":"2025-03-08T11:07:00","modified_gmt":"2025-03-08T07:07:00","slug":"nikah-man-strike-wife-not-best","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/10\/nikah-man-strike-wife-not-best\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Marriage: Men who hit their wives not the best"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Iyas ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Do not strike the maidens of Allah<\/strong>,\u201d but Umar came to the Prophet and he said, \u201cWomen have become emboldened toward their husbands.\u201d The Prophet gave them a concession to strike them lightly. Then, many women came to the family of the Prophet and complained about their husbands. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>Many women have come to the family of Muhammad complaining about their husbands. T<\/strong><strong>hese men are not the best among you<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2146<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Sahih<\/strong> <\/em>(authentic) according to Al-Arna&#8217;ut<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0625\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u062a\u064e\u0636\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0625\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u06