 Allah is the Lord of men and women. Adam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27174,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/02\/13\/huquq-husbands-mothers-greatest\/","url_meta":{"origin":9741,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Huquq: Rights of husbands and mothers are greatest","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: She said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, who among people has the greatest right over the wife?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHer husband.\u201d Aisha said, \u201cWho among people has the greatest right of the man?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHis mother.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak \u2018ala\u0301 al-S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323ayn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20492,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/28\/nikah-couples-similar-age\/","url_meta":{"origin":9741,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nikah: Marrying couples of similar age","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 28, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: Abu Bakr and Umar, may Allah be pleased with them, offered a marriage proposal to the Prophet\u2019s daughter Fatimah. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cShe is too young.\u201d Then, Ali proposed to Fatimah and the Prophet married her to him. Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisd